## File Naming Best Practices

### Ruby Files

```
# Models (singular)
user.rb
blog_post.rb
article_comment.rb

# Controllers (plural + controller suffix)
users_controller.rb
blog_posts_controller.rb
article_comments_controller.rb

# Jobs (singular + job suffix)
article_notification_job.rb
data_export_job.rb

# Mailers (singular + mailer suffix)
article_mailer.rb
user_mailer.rb
```

### View Files

```
# Actions (singular resource name)
articles/index.html.erb
articles/show.html.erb
articles/new.html.erb
articles/edit.html.erb

# Partials (starts with underscore)
articles/_form.html.erb
articles/_article.html.erb
shared/_header.html.erb
```

### JavaScript Files

```
# Stimulus controllers (snake_case + _controller suffix)
dropdown_controller.js
modal_controller.js
autosave_controller.js

# Other JS files (snake_case)
application.js
utilities.js
```

### Test Files

```
# Tests (matches class name + _test suffix)
user_test.rb
article_test.rb
articles_controller_test.rb
article_notification_job_test.rb
```

